  "html": "<div class=\"fr-view\"><div class=\"fr-view\"><p>The focus of this repetition is on these sentences:</p><p>Sentence 1 - これは なん ですか。(Kore wa nan deska?) = What is this?&nbsp;</p><p>Sentence 2 - ろせんず です。(rosenzu des) = It&#39;s a railway map.</p><p><strong style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">How to use this lesson -&nbsp;</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Please watch the video twice (first with the subtitles and then without them) and repeat the sentences.</span></p><p><span class=\"fr-video fr-fvc fr-dvb\"><iframe src=\"https://platform.thinkific.com/videoproxy/v1/play/bruiutkobr2ovlip5ha0\" scrolling=\"no\" class=\"videoproxy_embed\" title=\"*D1 L4 R1.mp4 - 00:11\" name=\"videoproxy_embed\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe></span><br></p></div></div>",
